AS Monaco Vice President Vadim Vasilyev has confirmed a bid for Russian attacking midfielder Aleksandr Golovin in an interview to Sport Express.<br />
<br />
&ldquo;We have made an offer for CSKA Moscow for Golovin. A more than generous offer. The contract length offered is 5 years. I think that a transition in a club like Monaco is best option for him, at this stage in his career. Everything should be decided in the coming days, maybe even today. We cannot wait long. If it does not come off, we will look to another option.&rdquo;

